== 批評 ==
因為人口成長和交通的便利，越來越多人可以進入以往不易進入的自然環境，當人數過多或是環境教育不足時，會對自然生態造成破壞。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsinenglish.no/2015/07/28/protests-fly-over-wild-camping/|title=Protests fly over ‘wild camping’|date=28 Jul 2015|publisher=NewsInEnglish.no|access-date=2015-08-27|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225140441/https://www.newsinenglish.no/2015/07/28/protests-fly-over-wild-camping/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

有些組織，如瑞典農夫協會（Lantbrukarnas Riksförbund），認為漫遊自由會干涉地主使用土地的權利，並且應排除商業活動。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lrf.se/politikochpaverkan/aganderatt-och-miljo/allemansratt/allemansratten-och-kommersiell-verksamhet/|access-date=2015-08-27|language=sv|title=Allemansrätten och kommersiell verksamhet|publisher=Lantbrukarnas Riksförbund|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029045751/https://www.lrf.se/politikochpaverkan/aganderatt-och-miljo/allemansratt/allemansratten-och-kommersiell-verksamhet/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.sweden.se/sustainability/2011/09/08/is-the-swedish-freedom-to-roam-too-generous/|access-date=2015-08-27|language=en|title=Is the Swedish freedom to roam too generous?|author=Sara Jeswani|date=2011-09-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305005101/http://blogs.sweden.se/sustainability/2011/09/08/is-the-swedish-freedom-to-roam-too-generous/|archivedate=2016-03-05}}</ref>

